==French==

===Etymology===
From earlier {{term|pluveir}} ← popular {{L.|fr}} {{term|plovere}} ← the classical verb {{term|pluere}}.

===Pronunciation===
*{{IPA|/plø.vwaʁ/}}
*[[w:SAMPA|SAMPA]]: /pl2.vwaR/

===Verb===
'''pleuvoir'''

# to [[rain]]

====Conjugation====
This is an [[impersonal verb]], only conjugated in the impersonal third person form (''[[il]]'').
 
